OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud mostly
OL,6,Fburning off this morning but may
OL,7,Flinger into the afternoon across
OL,8,Feastern Aberdeenshire. Otherwise dry
OL,9,Fwith some spells of sunshine. Warm
OL,10,Finland, east coast cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with some late sunshine
OL,13,Fthis evening but dull along the east
OL,14,Fcoast. The rest of the night will be
OL,15,Fdry with variable amounts of cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FIt will be dry with a fair
OL,18,Famount of cloud across the west. Some
OL,19,Fsunshine breaking through across the
OL,20,Feast. Breezy. Warm in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
