OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,7,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,8,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,9,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
